   2:main.c        ****  *
   3:main.c        ****  * Uses:
   4:main.c        ****  *  - adc_balanced.c/.h  : round-robin ADC sampling over AMux (N_CH channels)
   5:main.c        ****  *  - joystick.c/.h      : calibration + mapping (deadband, inversion, scaling)
   6:main.c        ****  *
   7:main.c        ****  * CLI stays here:
   8:main.c        ****  *   'c' : calibration advance (start -> center capture -> save)
   9:main.c        ****  *   'x' : stop streaming (and also cancels calibration if active)
  10:main.c        ****  *   's' : start streaming
  11:main.c        ****  */
